Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:09.71,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能感受到 肩負著重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.21,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}與　一起飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.21,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(596,12)}你
