Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.06,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能與　做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.06,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(625,12)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.15,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}繼續前進！繼續前進!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:36.11,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}與　一起飛翔到任何地方
